1. *Šerifa* sam upoznao prošlog leta. (I met a *sheriff* last summer.)
2. Na velikoj farmi, *šerif* je zadužen za održavanje reda. (On a large farm, the *sheriff* is responsible for maintaining order.)
3. Nekoliko *šerifa* patrolira gradom svake noći. (Several *sheriffs* patrol the city every night.)
4. *Šerife*, zar misliš da bi to bilo dobra ideja? (Sheriff, do you really think that would be a good idea?)
5. *Šerif* je uhvatio pljačkaša nakon žestoke potjere. (The *sheriff* caught the thief after a fierce chase.)
6. Stanovnici grada su imenovali *šerifu* da bude njihov predstavnik u pregovorima. (The city residents appointed the *sheriff* to be their representative in negotiations.)
7. *Šerifom* je postavljen veteran lokalne policije. (A veteran of the local police was appointed *sheriff*.)
8. *Šerifi* su se borili protiv divljaka na divljem zapadu. (The *sheriffs* fought against outlaws in the Wild West.)
9. Pitala sam *šerifa* da li su im potrebne dodatne snage za potragu. (I asked the *sheriff* if they needed additional forces for the search.)
10. *Šerifima* je bilo potrebno nekoliko sati da obuhvate sve ulice u potrazi za bjeguncem. (It took several hours for the *sheriffs* to cover all the streets in the search for the fugitive.)